channel.title: Compiling and Running server error... Help NEEDED
channel.description:
Ok I made a server using the Utorrent and I had it running for about five minutes then I made myself admin tryed to compile and it said it was invalid becuz i didnt have JDK 5.0 or 6.0. I have JDK 6u7 and have my Enviormental Variables set I have no-ip and everything. After I tried to compile and the error happened I tryed to click 'runserver' then it would open and close really fast. Please help, I will try to make a video to show you what's happening.
Thanks
Kind Regards, Zoro35
